  src/cli/error-guidance.ts,project,enhanced ownership_conflict guidance with audit flag recommendations
  tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts,project,updated close_through_update code assertion
close_reason: Update-command close and ownership error paths now produce structured actionable guidance with audit flag recommendations
